comments: Cousins (LAC) wraps his arm around Jokic's (DEN) opposite-side hip and the contact affects his FOM.
Cousins (LAC) reaches in and makes contact to Jokic's (DEN) arm and body that affects his SQBR.
Replay review of the foul on Cousins (LAC) pursuant to a coach's challenge is deemed unsuccessful.  Cousins makes contact to Jokic's body as he returns to the floor during his jump shot attempt.
Porter Jr. (DEN) makes contact to Jackson's (LAC) body before he returns to the floor and affects his jump shot attempt.
Gordon (DEN) briefly places a hand on Leonard (LAC) and marginal contact occurs during his putback shot attempt.
Rondo (LAC) commits a take foul on Gordon (DEN).
Jokic (DEN) reaches in and makes contact to Cousins' (LAC) arm prior to his shooting motion.

George (LAC) reaches in and marginal contact occurs with Jokic's (DEN) head after he releases the pass.   Contact to an opponent?s head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Batum (LAC) commits a take foul on Campazzo (DEN).
